---
---

<section class="cta-banner">
  <div class="cta-inner">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <div class="cta-prefix">&gt; speaking_invite.send()</div>
      <h2>Got a conference, podcast or event? <span class="highlight">Let's talk.</span></h2>
      <p>I speak about AI in production, MLOps under real constraints, and building engineering teams that ship. Happy to join meetups, panels, or keynotes — in person or remote.</p>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/speaking/">invite me to speak &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-banner {
    max-width: 1440px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 6rem) 4rem;
  }
  .cta-inner {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .cta-prefix {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .cta-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cta-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
